### Update a measurable habit

PUT localhost:30000/api/v1/habits/measurable/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginToken}}

{
    "label": "Drink water",
    "icon": 2,
    "step": 1,
    "unit": "cups"
}

###

### Reject a measurable habit update with domain validation errors

PUT localhost:30000/api/v1/habits/measurable/{{habitId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginToken}}

{
    "label": "@",
    "icon": 99,
    "step": 0,
    "unit": "K!"
}
